---
import step1Img from '@/assets/images/9d6d7d7068d0.jpeg';
import step2Img from '@/assets/images/8f8c6668ef95.jpeg';
import step3Img from '@/assets/images/6b91c35eb686.jpeg';
---

<section class="section section--tint prp-h-s7">
  <div class="container">

    <h2 class="prp-h-s7__heading">Your Platelet-Rich Plasma for Hair Restoration Journey</h2>

    <div class="prp-h-s7__steps">

      <div class="prp-h-s7__step">
        <div class="prp-h-s7__step-img-wrap">
          <img
            src={step1Img.src}
            alt="Man receiving hair restoration consultation at Menon Medispa"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            width="121"
            height="121"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="prp-h-s7__step-heading">Comprehensive Consultation</h3>
        <p class="prp-h-s7__step-body">We begin with a thorough evaluation of your hair loss pattern, medical history, and goals. This allows Dr. Menon to confirm you're a good candidate and customize your treatment plan.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prp-h-s7__step">
        <div class="prp-h-s7__step-img-wrap">
          <img
            src={step2Img.src}
            alt="Woman getting hair restoration PRP treatment at Menon Medispa"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            width="121"
            height="121"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="prp-h-s7__step-heading">Customized Treatment Session</h3>
        <p class="prp-h-s7__step-body">A small amount of blood is drawn and placed in a centrifuge to isolate the platelet-rich plasma. Dr. Menon then precisely injects the PRP into targeted areas of your scalp using a fine needle. The procedure typically takes about 60-90 minutes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prp-h-s7__step">
        <div class="prp-h-s7__step-img-wrap">
          <img
            src={step3Img.src}
            alt="Before and after woman hair restoration results at Menon Medispa"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            width="121"
            height="121"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="prp-h-s7__step-heading">Progressive Results &amp; Maintenance</h3>
        <p class="prp-h-s7__step-body">Initial improvements in hair thickness and reduced shedding are typically noticed within 2-3 months. For optimal results, a series of 3 treatments spaced 4-6 weeks apart is recommended, followed by maintenance sessions.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .prp-h-s7__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .prp-h-s7__steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .prp-h-s7__step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .prp-h-s7__step-img-wrap {
    width: 121px;
    height: 121px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .prp-h-s7__step-img-wrap img {
    width: 121px;
    height: 121px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .prp-h-s7__step-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .prp-h-s7__step-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .prp-h-s7__steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }
  }
</style>
